        "email": "maloo@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2012-04-03 05:42:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/903dc492-7d4d-11e1-aaf6-525400d2bfa6).  Ran 15 tests.  2 tests failed: replay-single, sanity.",
